Portfolio (React + Vite)

This repo is now a single-page portfolio built with React (JSX) and Vite.

Structure
- `src/` contains the React app (one page with sections: Home, About, Portfolio, Contact).
- `public/` contains static assets copied into the build output:
	- `public/CSS/Project.css` (your existing stylesheet)
	- `public/Images/` (images)
	- `public/cv.html` (separate CV page for download/print)
	- `public/app.js` (theme persistence + small UI helpers)
- `legacy/` contains the old multi-page HTML files for reference.

Run locally
- Install: `npm install`
- Dev server: `npm run dev`
- Build: `npm run build`
- Preview build: `npm run preview`

Deploy (Netlify)
- Build command: `npm run build`
- Publish directory: `dist`